  "descriptionHtml": "<p data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"264\"><strong data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"264\">Studio Garden – Praticidade, design e lazer completo no coração de Florianópolis</strong></p>\n<p data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"503\">Este <strong data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"293\">Studio garden</strong>  é a escolha ideal para quem busca um estilo de vida moderno, funcional e com muito conforto.  Possui <strong data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"502\">1 vaga de garagem privativa</strong>.</p>\n<p data-start=\"505\" data-end=\"710\">Localizado em um dos empreendimentos mais inovadores da cidade, oferece uma <strong data-start=\"594\" data-end=\"649\">infraestrutura de lazer e conveniência incomparável</strong>, com espaços pensados para o dia a dia dinâmico e conectado:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"1282\">\n<li data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"741\">\n<p data-start=\"714\" data-end=\"741\">Hall de entrada com estar</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"742\" data-end=\"788\">\n<p data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"788\"><strong data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"758\">Homemarket</strong> (minimercado no condomínio)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"789\" data-end=\"851\">\n<p data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"851\"><strong data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"809\">Delivery Space</strong> (espaço para recebimento de encomendas)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"879\">\n<p data-start=\"854\" data-end=\"879\"><strong data-start=\"854\" data-end=\"877\">Coworking mobiliado</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"901\">\n<p data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"901\"><strong data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"899\">Sala de jogos</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"934\">\n<p data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"934\"><strong data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"932\">Lavanderia compartilhada</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"935\" data-end=\"955\">\n<p data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"955\"><strong data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"953\">Espaço Clean</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"974\">\n<p data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"974\"><strong data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"972\">Sky Lounge</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"998\">\n<p data-start=\"977\" data-end=\"998\"><strong data-start=\"977\" data-end=\"996\">Salão de festas</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"999\" data-end=\"1020\">\n<p data-start=\"1001\" data-end=\"1020\"><strong data-start=\"1001\" data-end=\"1018\">Salão Gourmet</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1021\" data-end=\"1064\">\n<p data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1064\"><strong data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1041\">Rooftop Lounge</strong> com vista panorâmica</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1065\" data-end=\"1082\">\n<p data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1082\"><strong data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1080\">Pet Place</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1083\" data-end=\"1106\">\n<p data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1106\"><strong data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1104\">Ateliê Infantil</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1131\">\n<p data-start=\"1109\" data-end=\"1131\"><strong data-start=\"1109\" data-end=\"1129\">Piscina com deck</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1169\">\n<p data-start=\"1134\" data-end=\"1169\"><strong data-start=\"1134\" data-end=\"1167\">Quadra poliesportiva de areia</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1170\" data-end=\"1214\">\n<p data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1214\"><strong data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1212\">Academia (fitness interno e externo)</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1215\" data-end=\"1235\">\n<p data-start=\"1217\" data-end=\"1235\"><strong data-start=\"1217\" data-end=\"1233\">Espaço Grill</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1236\" data-end=\"1265\">\n<p data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1265\"><strong data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1263\">Oficina compartilhada</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1266\" data-end=\"1282\">\n<p data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1282\"><strong data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1282\">Bike Share</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1284\" data-end=\"1483\">Além de todos esses diferenciais, o empreendimento está situado em uma região de alta valorização e demanda, sendo uma excelente opção tanto para moradia quanto para investimento com foco em locação.</p>",
